# Git Attributes Configuration
# Manages line ending normalization and file type classification
# Documentation: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitattributes

# Line ending strategy:
# - Text files: Normalize to LF on commit, preserve on checkout
# - Binary files: Never modify
# - Default: Let Git auto-detect (text=auto disabled to prevent issues)
#
# Note: text=auto can cause problems with web-editable files where
# line endings may change outside of Git's control

# Text files - normalize line endings (CRLF â†’ LF)

